# "Fell in love with coser 4" is a live-action video interactive game.
<!--text-->
"Fell in love with coser 4" is a live-action video interactive game.
The game takes you into the world of the main character, where you have complex interactions with 10 beautiful women, and this game does not contain romantic elements and a touching plot.

"Fell in love with coser 4" is the fourth live-action video interactive game shot by Thermae Studio, first of all, thank you for the support and encouragement of players, the game theme is relatively niche, destined not to be liked by most people, if you are eager to experience love or rich plot, it is obvious that you chose the wrong game, the producer of the game does not understand love at all, can not do the touching love story of friends, and there is no money for various scene layout, and this game is the lowest production cost in the world's similar games, The game with the worst story! (Dissatisfied)
The only thing to be thankful for is that the producers still use all the steel on the blade, and if you're a fan of blades, then I promise you'll collect all of my games without exception!
I hope that this "Fell in love with coser 4" will not disappoint old players, and I hope to open a window for new players! If you are looking for pure love, please do not play this game, because this game will not only ruin your purity, but also make you lose interest in pure love!
